quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  28,60,"Wama ooteetum min shay-in famataAAualhayati addunya wazeenatuhawama AAinda Allahi khayrun waabqa afalataAAqiloon"
  28,61,"Afaman waAAadnahu waAAdan hasananfahuwa laqeehi kaman mattaAAnahu mataAAa alhayatiaddunya thumma huwa yawma alqiyamati minaalmuhdareen"
  28,62,"Wayawma yunadeehim fayaqoolu aynashuraka-iya allatheena kuntum tazAAumoon"
  28,63,"Qala allatheena haqqaAAalayhimu alqawlu rabbana haola-i allatheenaaghwayna aghwaynahum kama ghawaynatabarra/na ilayka ma kanoo iyyanayaAAbudoon"
  28,64,"Waqeela odAAoo shurakaakumfadaAAawhum falam yastajeeboo lahum waraawoo alAAathabalaw annahum kanoo yahtadoon"
  28,65,"Wayawma yunadeehim fayaqoolu mathaajabtumu almursaleen"
  28,66,"FaAAamiyat AAalayhimu al-anbaoyawma-ithin fahum la yatasaaloon"
  28,67,"Faamma man taba waamanawaAAamila salihan faAAasa an yakoona minaalmufliheen"
  28,68,"Warabbuka yakhluqu ma yashaowayakhtaru ma kana lahumu alkhiyaratu subhanaAllahi wataAAala AAamma yushrikoon"
  28,69,"Warabbuka yaAAlamu ma tukinnu sudooruhumwama yuAAlinoon"
  28,70,"Wahuwa Allahu la ilahailla huwa lahu alhamdu fee al-oola wal-akhiratiwalahu alhukmu wa-ilayhi turjaAAoon"
